th-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-silver&amp;subId3=xid:fr1614043017334djf\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-orig-url=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11F0LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-silver\" data-ml-id=\"8\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1614043017334djf\">Silver&nbsp;</a>($230 less than a new version)</p></li><li><p>$1,609: 1TB SSD and 16GB memory in<a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11F3LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-silver&amp;subId3=xid:fr1614043017334adi\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-orig-url=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11F3LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-silver\" data-ml-id=\"9\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1614043017334adi\"> Silver</a> ($290 less than a new version)</p></li><li><p>$1,779:&nbsp;2TB SSD and 8GB memory in <a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11C1LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-space-gray&amp;subId3=xid:fr1614043017335dea\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-orig-url=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11C1LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-space-gray\" data-ml-id=\"10\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1614043017335dea\">Space Gray&nbsp;</a>($320 less than a new version)</p></li><li><p>$1,949:&nbsp;2TB SSD and 16GB of memory in <a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11C4LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-space-gray&amp;subId3=xid:fr1614043017335hjh\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-orig-url=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11C4LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-space-gray\" data-ml-id=\"11\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1614043017335hjh\">Space Gray</a> or <a href=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11F4LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-silver&amp;subId3=xid:fr1614043017335eae\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-orig-url=\"https://apple.sjv.io/c/321564/435031/7613?subid1=US-002-3608971-000-000000-web&amp;u=https://www.apple.com/shop/product/G11F4LL/A/refurbished-133-inch-macbook-pro-apple-m1-chip-with-8%E2%80%91core-cpu-and-8%E2%80%91core-gpu-silver\" data-ml-id=\"12\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1614043017335eae\">Silver</a>&nbsp;($350 less than a new version)</p></li></ul><p>All refurbished Macs come with a standard one-year warranty. You can learn more about Apple's refurbished items in our <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/3238012/how-to-buy-refurbished-macbook-refurbished-iphone-refurbished-ipad.html?page=2\">FAQ</a>.</p><p>The 13-inch M1 MacBook Pro is often on sale at third-party retailers such as Best Buy, Amazon, and others. But usually, they sell standard configuration models with 8GB of memory and a 256GB or 512GB SSD. The refurbished store is a good way to save money on models with more memory and higher-capacity SSDs. For example, you can get a refurbished model with a 2TB SSD and 16GB of memory for $1,949. That's a $350 savings that's significant.</p><div><p><img onclick=\"jwplayer(